data.description: WELCOME HOME to this Cozy and Well Maintained 2 Bedroom, 1 1/2 Bath, 1 Car Garage Home on a Spacious, Completely Fenced Lot in Aloha Gardens. Minutes from the Famous Tarpon Springs Sponge Docks and Centrally Located Near ALL Major Roadways, traveling to Tampa/St Pete/Clearwater is a Breeze!  Upon arriving you will walk up to and LOVE the spacious Front Porch where you can sit and relax after a long day.  Inside you will be greeted with Large Ceramic Tiles that flow throughout the Living area with Beautiful Laminate Plank Flooring in both Bedrooms.  A new Upgraded Dimensional Shingle Roof as well as New Gutters were just installed in the Fall of 2022.  A Stylish Kitchen with Granite Tile Counters, Stainless Steel appliances, White upper Cabinetry with Beautiful Gray Lower and a Granite Top Kitchen Island for added Storage and Space. This Gem has both a Front Living Room as well as a Rear Family Room which is so accommodating for those who wish to watch TV in one and Read a Book in the other. The Main Bath has been totally remodeled with Beautiful Shower Tiles, Stylish Vanity with Fixtures, and Lighting. The screened in Patio leads to a Spacious, Completely Fenced Backyard which offers a stone pavered path to a Large Covered Gazebo which is great for entertaining. Enjoy time outdoors with Barbequing with Friends and Family.  This home is located minutes away from Shopping, Restaurants, Parks, Beaches, anything you may need. Come view this Beauty Today!!
